$ON_FLDFIFCP
Onevent AFTER_CHANGE Gosub AMM_FLDFIFCP From W2BAN2
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_FLDFIFCP(zc) From W2BAN2
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_FLDFIFCP(zc) From W2BAN2
Return

Subprog D_FLDFIFCP(VALEUR)
